measurements.description: Approximately one thousand four hundred fifty tiny flowers and approximately 1200 buds on 18 14-cm branched inflorescences; 8 immature inflorescences; 47x22-cm plant, foliage in excellent condition, grown on 9x14-cm cork slab; dorsal sepal violet; lateral sepals white, overlaid violet proximally; petals violet; lip white, spur violet; substance not described; texture matte.
